---
/**
 * /about — Public about page
 */
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import PublicNav from '../components/PublicNav.astro';
---
<Layout title="About">
  <Fragment slot="header-action">
    <PublicNav current="about" />
  </Fragment>

  <h1>About Bespoke Dog Adventures</h1>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
      Bespoke Dog Adventures started with a simple idea: dogs deserve more than
      a quick walk around the block. They deserve real outdoor experiences that
      match their energy and curiosity. What began as adventures with a few
      neighborhood dogs has grown into a trusted, membership-based service across
      West LA.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Safety First</h2>
    <p>
      Every adventure is carefully planned with safety as the top priority. We
      keep groups small so each dog gets individual attention. We carry water,
      first aid supplies, and always have a plan. We get to know every dog's
      temperament, triggers, and needs before the first hike.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>How Adventures Work</h2>
    <p>
      We offer 2-hour and 4-hour adventures through trails, beaches, and open
      spaces across West LA, Venice, Playa Vista, Marina del Rey, and El Segundo.
      Each outing is tailored to the group — we match dogs by energy level and
      temperament so everyone has a great time.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Pickup & Drop-off</h2>
    <p>
      We pick up and drop off your dog right at your door. You provide any gate
      codes or special instructions during onboarding, and we handle the rest.
      You'll receive photos and updates during every adventure so you always know
      your dog is having a blast.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div style="text-align:center; padding: 1rem 0;">
    <a href="/request" class="btn btn-primary">Request Membership</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
